EASEL ON


          Primary Account Relationship Code - Help

    This option allows accounts into a relationship from only
    customers whose relationship with the primary account meets
    the criteria defined in this relationship code table.
    The specific RCIF relationship codes must be defined on
    the MICM Record 7104 (Customer Relationship Codes).
